snippet.title: Eternal Ring Trailer
snippet.description:
This is from PS2 demo disc From Software First Previews. It's a Japanese Only demo disc that you could only get in the Playstation Festival 2000.

This trailer is for Eternal Ring.

Notes from Uploader:
This is pretty cool, for something made in 2000 for the PS2.
Not much i can say outside of it looks cool.
